          &lt;% end %&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
      &lt;% end %&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;
  &lt;% end %&gt;
```

**app/views/categories/_category_depth_0.html.erb**
```
&lt;header class=&quot;app-card-header&quot;&gt;
